      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to the Navier-Stokes and scalar transport equations implemented in the hemolysis damage model. Observed order of accuracy (1.97 for velocity, 1.94 for scalar) consistent with second-order spatial discretization. Results documented in verification report NCV-2024-003.",
