      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison metric (E_rms) computed between CFD NIH predictions and experimental NIH measurements across all 5 operating points. E_rms = 8.4%, within the 15% acceptance threshold. Uncertainty in experimental NIH (U_exp = ±12%) accounted for in comparison; all CFD predictions fall within experimental uncertainty bands.",
