      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same device class and flow regime as the COU. Operating conditions in validation span the full COU operating envelope. Validation scenario relevance score assessed via Morrison Table 4 criteria: geometry similarity = high, flow regime = matched, fluid properties = matched within stated bounds.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
