      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis data collected from n=6 replicate pump units per operating point; inter-unit variability (CV < 8%) and intra-run variability (CV < 5%) documented. Sample size justified via power analysis targeting 80% power at α=0.05 for detecting 15% NIH difference. All samples from the same manufacturing lot with documented traceability.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
        "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/ac/test-samples-mrl5",
