      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Equivalency matrix (EQM-2024-COU2) documents mapping between experimental boundary conditions and CFD inputs for all 5 operating points. Inlet velocity profiles measured via PIV and applied as CFD boundary conditions. Blood viscosity matched within ±3% via rheometry. Geometric fidelity confirmed via CMM scan of pump impeller (maximum deviation 0.03 mm from CAD nominal).",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
